These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 3

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-1::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: fanta, soy-milk
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: old-henry, blend
The people have 2 different hobbies: traveling, hiking
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, bike
1. the blend-smoker is on the left or right of the person drinking fanta##3
2. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the blend-smoker##1
3. the person driving the bike is on the right of the person who's hobby is traveling##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |
| Beverage      | soy-milk      | fanta    |
| Cigar           | blend | old-henry |
| Hobby   | traveling       | hiking  |
| Transport     | airplane      | bike     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-2::.
There 2 different types of food: cauliflower, watermelon
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: mystery, adventure
2 different pets are kept: cat, rabbit
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: august, february
1. the owner of the cat is on the left or right of the person who's birthday is in february##3
2. the person eating watermelon is on the left of the person watching adventure movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in february is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |
| Food          | watermelon | cauliflower |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery       | adventure         |
| Pet           | rabbit     | cat         |
| Birthday     | february    | august    |

