.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-3::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: board-games, hiking
City: nizza, paris
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: folk, r&b
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: dahlia, balloon-flower
1. the fan of r&b is on the far right##1
2. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left of the person traveling to nizza##1
3. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left or right of the person who growsdahlia##3
4. the person who growsballoon-flower is on the left of the fan of r&b##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |        1        |      2      |
| Hobby         | hiking          | board-games |
| City           | paris | nizza     |
| Music-Genre   | folk            | r&b         |
| Flower     | balloon-flower         | dahlia   |

