The people use 2 different means of transport: tram, taxi
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: disco, trance
The people have 2 different jobs:  firefighter, architect
1. the fan of disco is on the left or right of the architect##3
2. the person drinking tea is the firefighter##1
3. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |
| Beverage      | tea     | cola   |
| Transport   | taxi    | tram |
| Music-Genre   | disco   | trance |
| Job           | firefighter | architect    |

