.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-3-20::.
2 different pets are kept: hedgehog, cat
There 2 different types of food: eggplant, papaya
There are 2 different favourite colors: orange, pink
The people use 2 different means of transport: airplane, taxi
1. the person who likes pink is on the left of the owner of the hedgehog##1
2. the person eating eggplant is the person who likes orange##1
3. the person who likes orange is the person driving the taxi##1
4. the person driving the airplane is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2     |
| Pet      | cat     | hedgehog |
| Food          | papaya   | eggplant |
| Color   | pink     | orange     |
| Transport     | airplane | taxi     |

 